// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2403 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: dae8e919-2c29-5c5c-b34d-6c1776f79132

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
